title: Big Bank, DJ Scream, Hoodrich Pablo Juan - Real Talk!

description:
Big Bank and DJ Scream discuss Donald Trump, how not to fall off in the rap game and more. Hoodrich Pablo Juan joins the show at the 35 minute mark for an exclusive, in depth interview about the music game and the streets!
